      "\n  apply Set.Subset.antisymm\n  آ· -- Prove the forward inclusion: if (xâ‚پ, xâ‚‚, xâ‚ƒ, xâ‚„, xâ‚…) satisfies the conditions, then xâ‚پ = xâ‚‚ = xâ‚ƒ = xâ‚„ = xâ‚…\n    intro âں¨xâ‚پ, xâ‚‚, xâ‚ƒ, xâ‚„, xâ‚…âں© h\n    simp only [Set.mem_setOf_eq, Set.mem_setOf_eq] at h âٹ¢\n    have hâ‚پ : 0 < xâ‚پ := by linarith\n    have hâ‚‚ : 0 < xâ‚‚ := by linarith\n    have hâ‚ƒ : 0 < xâ‚ƒ := by linarith\n    have hâ‚„ : 0 < xâ‚„ := by linarith\n    have hâ‚… : 0 < xâ‚… := by linarith\n    have hâ‚† : (xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) * (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) â‰¤ 0 := by\n      linarith\n    have hâ‚‡ : (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) * (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) â‰¤ 0 := by\n      linarith\n    have hâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) * (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) â‰¤ 0 := by\n      linarith\n    have hâ‚‰ : (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚پ * xâ‚ƒ) * (xâ‚… ^ 2 - xâ‚پ * xâ‚ƒ) â‰¤ 0 := by\n      linarith\n    have hâ‚پâ‚€ : (xâ‚… ^ 2 - xâ‚‚ * xâ‚„) * (xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚‚ * xâ‚„) â‰¤ 0 := by\n      linarith\n    -- Use the fact that the product is non-positive to deduce the equalities\n    have hâ‚پâ‚پ : xâ‚پ = xâ‚‚ := by\n      -- Detailed proof to deduce xâ‚پ = xâ‚‚\n      by_contra hâ‚پâ‚پ\n      have hâ‚پâ‚‚ : xâ‚پ â‰  xâ‚‚ := hâ‚پâ‚پ\n      have hâ‚پâ‚ƒ : (xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) * (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) â‰¤ 0 := hâ‚†\n      have hâ‚پâ‚„ : xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… = 0 := by\n        by_cases hâ‚پâ‚„ : xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… = 0\n        آ· exact hâ‚پâ‚„\n        آ· have hâ‚پâ‚… : xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… > 0 âˆ¨ xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… < 0 := by\n            cases' lt_or_gt_of_ne hâ‚پâ‚„ with hâ‚پâ‚„ hâ‚پâ‚„\n            آ· exact Or.inr hâ‚پâ‚„\n            آ· exact Or.inl hâ‚پâ‚„\n          cases' hâ‚پâ‚… with hâ‚پâ‚… hâ‚پâ‚…\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚پ^2 - xâ‚ƒxâ‚… > 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚† : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) * (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) > 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚پ^2 - xâ‚ƒxâ‚… < 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚† : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… â‰¥ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) * (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) < 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n        <;> simp_all\n        <;> nlinarith\n      have hâ‚پâ‚… : (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚…) = 0 := by\n        by_cases hâ‚پâ‚… : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… = 0\n        آ· exact hâ‚پâ‚…\n        آ· have hâ‚پâ‚† : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… > 0 âˆ¨ xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… < 0 := by\n            cases' lt_or_gt_of_ne hâ‚پâ‚… with hâ‚پâ‚… hâ‚پâ‚…\n            آ· exact Or.inr hâ‚پâ‚…\n            آ· exact Or.inl hâ‚پâ‚…\n          cases' hâ‚پâ‚† with hâ‚پâ‚† hâ‚پâ‚†\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚‚^2 - xâ‚ƒxâ‚… > 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) > 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚‚^2 - xâ‚ƒxâ‚… < 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : xâ‚پ ^ 2 - xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… â‰¥ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) < 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n        <;> simp_all\n        <;> nlinarith\n      have hâ‚پâ‚† : xâ‚پ ^ 2 = xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… := by linarith\n      have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 = xâ‚ƒ * xâ‚… := by linarith\n      have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : xâ‚پ ^ 2 = xâ‚‚ ^ 2 := by linarith\n      have hâ‚پâ‚‰ : xâ‚پ = xâ‚‚ âˆ¨ xâ‚پ = -xâ‚‚ := by\n        apply or_iff_not_imp_left.mpr\n        intro hâ‚پâ‚‰\n        apply eq_of_sub_eq_zero\n        apply mul_left_cancelâ‚€ (sub_ne_zero.mpr hâ‚پâ‚‰)\n        nlinarith\n      cases' hâ‚پâ‚‰ with hâ‚پâ‚‰ hâ‚پâ‚‰\n      آ· exfalso\n        exact hâ‚پâ‚‚ hâ‚پâ‚‰\n      آ· have hâ‚‚â‚€ : xâ‚پ > 0 := by linarith\n        have hâ‚‚â‚پ : xâ‚‚ > 0 := by linarith\n        have hâ‚‚â‚‚ : xâ‚پ = -xâ‚‚ := hâ‚پâ‚‰\n        nlinarith\n      <;> simp_all\n      <;> nlinarith\n    have hâ‚پâ‚‚ : xâ‚‚ = xâ‚ƒ := by\n      -- Detailed proof to deduce xâ‚‚ = xâ‚ƒ\n      by_contra hâ‚پâ‚‚\n      have hâ‚پâ‚ƒ : xâ‚‚ â‰  xâ‚ƒ := hâ‚پâ‚‚\n      have hâ‚پâ‚„ : (xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) * (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) â‰¤ 0 := hâ‚‡\n      have hâ‚پâ‚… : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ = 0 := by\n        by_cases hâ‚پâ‚… : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ = 0\n        آ· exact hâ‚پâ‚…\n        آ· have hâ‚پâ‚† : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ > 0 âˆ¨ xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ < 0 := by\n            cases' lt_or_gt_of_ne hâ‚پâ‚… with hâ‚پâ‚… hâ‚پâ‚…\n            آ· exact Or.inr hâ‚پâ‚…\n            آ· exact Or.inl hâ‚پâ‚…\n          cases' hâ‚پâ‚† with hâ‚پâ‚† hâ‚پâ‚†\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚‚^2 - xâ‚„xâ‚پ > 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) * (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‰ : (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) > 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚‚^2 - xâ‚„xâ‚پ < 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ â‰¥ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) * (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‰ : (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) < 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n        <;> simp_all\n        <;> nlinarith\n      have hâ‚پâ‚† : (xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ) = 0 := by\n        by_cases hâ‚پâ‚† : xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ = 0\n        آ· exact hâ‚پâ‚†\n        آ· have hâ‚پâ‚‡ : xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ > 0 âˆ¨ xâ‚ƒ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ < 0 := by\n            cases' lt_or_gt_of_ne hâ‚پâ‚† with hâ‚پâ‚† hâ‚پâ‚†\n            آ· exact Or.inr hâ‚پâ‚†\n            آ· exact Or.inl hâ‚پâ‚†\n          cases' hâ‚پâ‚‡ with hâ‚پâ‚‡ hâ‚پâ‚‡\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚ƒ^2 - xâ‚„xâ‚پ > 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ â‰¤ 0 := by\n              nlinarith\n            have hâ‚پâ‚‰ : (xâ‚„ ^ 2 - xâ‚… * xâ‚‚) > 0 := by\n              nlinarith [sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚پ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚‚, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚ƒ, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚„, sq_pos_of_pos hâ‚…]\n            nlinarith\n          آ· -- Case: xâ‚ƒ^2 - xâ‚„xâ‚پ < 0\n            have hâ‚پâ‚ˆ : xâ‚‚ ^ 2 - xâ‚„ * xâ‚پ",
      "it's better to note that for each term like `(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)`, it also appears in another inequality.\n\nActually, `(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)` appears in `(xâ‚„آ² - xâ‚پxâ‚ƒ)(xâ‚…آ² - xâ‚پxâ‚ƒ)` only if we consider `xâ‚پxâ‚ƒ`, no. \n\nActually, the correct observation is:\n\nThe term `xâ‚پآ²` appears in `(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)` and `(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚‚xâ‚„)`.\nBut perhaps not directly helpful.\n\nBut looking better, the product is:\n`P = (xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)(xâ‚‚آ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…) (xâ‚‚آ² - xâ‚„xâ‚پ)(xâ‚ƒآ² - xâ‚„xâ‚پ) (xâ‚ƒآ² - xâ‚…xâ‚‚)(xâ‚„آ² - xâ‚…xâ‚‚) (xâ‚„آ² - xâ‚پxâ‚ƒ)(xâ‚…آ² - xâ‚پxâ‚ƒ) (xâ‚…آ² - xâ‚‚xâ‚„)(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚‚xâ‚„)`.\n\nNow, let me try to pair the terms:\n\nNotice that `(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)` is paired with `(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚‚xâ‚„)` (both involve `xâ‚پآ²`).\n\nBut overall, it's not straightforward to see squares.\n\nBut let me try to multiply the first and last inequalities:\n\n`[(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)(xâ‚‚آ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)] * [(xâ‚…آ² - xâ‚‚xâ‚„)(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚‚xâ‚„)] â‰¤ 0`.\nBut if we think of this as `(a)(b)(c)(a)`, no, that doesn't work. \n\nActually, better:\n\nThe product of all factors is:\n`(xâ‚پآ² - xâ‚ƒxâ‚…)(xâ‚‚آ² - xâ‚ƒx",
      "â‚ƒ",
